@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

###
# 1. Register a user (Signup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
# 2. Login user
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
# Extract token from the login response for the next request
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YzdjMTU5NTQxZTA3N2I0YzY3NDFlMiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NDcwNDQxNywiZXhwIjoxNzc1MzA5MjE3fQ.CiuBBSNu9Ftx-GoOTIuvM-TaRhbptTNuxvqMJ-sZT9s
###
# 3. Get current user profile (Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# 4. Chat with Claude AI (Phase 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "Who does land in Ghana belong to?"
}

###
# 5. Extract Text from Document (Phase 4)
# You need a valid file path in the local directory (e.g., sample.pdf)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ocr/extract
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="document"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###
# 6. Analyze Document with Claude (Phase 4)
# You need a valid file path in the local directory (e.g., sample.pdf)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ocr/analyze
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message"

Can you summarize the main legal points in this document?
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="document"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###
# 7. Get All Chat Sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# 8. Get Chat History for specific session
# Replace <SESSION_ID> with the id from the above request
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/history/<SESSION_ID>?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# 9. Chat with Simple Explanation Mode and Session Continuation
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat?mode=simple
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "hello.",
  "sessionId": "replace_with_valid_session_id_if_continuing_chat"
}
